rows.label: fev01_070_110_msg0001
rows.name:
Hey there, Rex. Curious
about that ship?

rows.label: fev01_070_110_msg0003
rows.name:
How could anyone not be
interested in it...

rows.label: fev01_070_110_msg0004
rows.name:
A ship this massive that isn't
powered by a Divine Beast...
that's really something.

rows.label: fev01_070_110_msg0005
rows.name:
I can't even begin to imagine
how the whole thing works.

rows.label: fev01_070_110_msg0007
rows.name: Who does this ship belong to?

rows.label: fev01_070_110_msg0008
rows.name:
It's owned by some guest of the
Chairman, I think... but I don't
know much beyond that.

rows.label: fev01_070_110_msg0010
rows.name:
I know you're curious, but
don't go climbing on board
or anything, okay?

rows.label: fev01_070_110_msg0012
rows.name:
Anyway, I need to get
back to my duties.
